{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"00b590f2f9","title":"关于文艺工作的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4750a5dbc8","index":0,"year":1975,"month":7,"day":14,"articleId":"00b590f2f9","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"文学艺术","id":"5387dec24b","type":"主题"},{"name":"周扬","id":"9c0e44d48c","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ea3032c03e","type":"title","text":"关于文艺工作的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e895bc8331","type":"paragraph","text":"关于文艺工作的谈话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1faecaba25","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"574bdfca92","type":"paragraph","text":"1975.07.14","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e5215a5d26","type":"paragraph","text":"党的文艺政策应该调整一下，一年、两年、三年，逐步逐步扩大文艺节目。缺少诗歌，缺少小说，缺少散文，缺少文艺评论。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"75bce4a732","type":"paragraph","text":"对于作家，要惩前毖后、治病救人，如果不是暗藏的有严重反革命行为的反革命分子，就要帮助。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f2d165be72","type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅那时被攻击，有胡适、创造社、太阳社、新月社、国民党。鲁迅在的话，不会赞成把周扬这些人长期关起来。脱离群众。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c6c348ab0f","type":"paragraph","text":"已经有了《红楼梦》、《水浒》，发行了。不能急，一两年之内逐步活跃起来，三年、四年、五年也好嘛。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7b60f48a09","type":"paragraph","text":"我们怕什么？一九五七年右派猖狂进攻，我们把他们骂我们的话登在报上，最后还是被我们打退了。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"83d49d2f85","type":"paragraph","text":"以前的《万水千山》没有二、四方面军，这不好。现在听说改好了。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8254588508","type":"paragraph","text":"文艺问题是思想问题，但是不能急，人民不看到材料，就无法评论。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa456a8ffb","type":"paragraph","text":"《反杜林论》，柏林大学撤了杜林的职，恩格斯不高兴了，争论是争论嘛，为什么撤职？杜林这个人活了八十多岁，名誉不好。处分人要注意，动不动就要撤职，动不动就要关起来，表现是神经衰弱症。林彪不跑，我们也不会杀他，批是要批的。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c45a8d8cb9","type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石的时候，报纸、广播、学校、电影都是他们的，他们蒙蔽人民。我们都是从那儿来的。我学孔夫子、资本家十三年，就是不知道马列，十月革命后才学马列，过去不知道。反动派没有多少威力，靠剥削过生活，他的兵都是靠抓壮丁，所以我们不怕他们。怕死的是林彪，叫他打锦州，他不打，最后两天他去了，俘虏十万人。又消灭了廖耀湘。长春沈阳解放。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"77f48022e4","type":"paragraph","text":"释放俘虏放得好，国民党怕得很。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00b590f2f9","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}